+- M06-FR-007/008: F creates protected one-package/one-PoA rows, exact projections, real stamp/notary
+  and signature checks, and retained draft races. Canonical sanction, security owner, terminal
+  activation, immutable consumed evidence, and public generation/activation proof remain partial
+  until 008F2.
+- M06-FR-009: G enforces frozen true subsidiary applicability and exact borrower/nominee signatures
+  with no readiness/repayment side effects. Consumed-signature immutability, action shape, public
+  generation, and authoritative PostgreSQL race remain partial until 008G2.
