- Queue dependency drain, JSON, protected-path, status-transition, whitespace, and diff checks
- Diff size: 9 non-Ralph files and 411 lines, below the 30-file/2,000-line limits

The complete outcome is in the [review packet](/Users/amitkallapa/LMS/.ralph/worktrees/2026-07-14_185927_architecture_review/.ralph/runs/2026-07-14_185927_architecture_review/review-packet.md). State, progress, handoff, digest, risk assessment, evidence, and changed-file inventory were finalized. No commit, merge, or push was performed.
